doctype html
html
  head
    style(type="text/css"): :stylus
      html,body { width: 100%; height: 100% }
      body { background: none;color:#222;background-size:cover }
      .vertical-center
        width: 100%
        height: 100%
        white-space: nowrap
        text-align: center
        font-size: 1.5em
        font-family: arial,sans-serif
      .vertical-center > *
        vertical-align: middle
        white-space: normal
        display: inline-block
      .vertical-center:before
        content: ""
        display: inline-block
        vertical-align: middle
        width: 0
        height: 100%

  body
    .vertical-center: div
      h1(style="margin:0 0 10px;line-height:1em") 網站掛掉了
      p(style="margin:0 0 20px;font-weight:100;color:#777") 很抱歉！服務暫時無法正確運行。說不定稍候就會回復正常了，請晚點再回來看看吧！
      a(onclick="window.location.reload()") 再試一次

